    <ul>
      <li><a href="/everyday-calculators/tip-calculator/">Tip Calculator</a> &ndash; Calculate tips and split bills for restaurants and services.</li>
      <li><a href="/everyday-calculators/discount-calculator/">Discount Calculator</a> &ndash; Calculate sale prices, savings, and final costs after discounts.</li>
